dct_title_s: Brookwood, Jackson Township, New Jersey 1962 section 4A
dct_description_sm: Map of Brookwood, Section 4A Jackson Township, Ocean County, N.J. along with inset map of township. Map features a two tables of curve data and official approvals and signatures from the municipal engineer and clerk.
